{"tid":1594911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟戰 - 提高經營成本","createTime":"2019-09-25T19:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T20:18:49.000Z","uid":260793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6eeec7a25041a3e55f99290087ec1620f79cd878","tid":1594911,"uid":260793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T19:59:14.000Z","msg":"除左罷買罷食呢種被動既抵制方法<br />\n最近見都有好多創新方法，例如排隊拎飛都但唔出現，book枱唔去<br />\n我覺得可以集思廣益點進一步提高對家經營成本<br />\n即係要佢付出左成本但收唔到回報<br />\n<br />\n細個整蠱人會人幫人叫外賣，係煩到假叫外賣既人，但實際上最大損失係商家<br />\n<br />\n假設外賣仔人數有限，而lunch hour 亦逼係固定時間<br />\n送外賣既速度變左其中一個幫唔幫襯既元素<br />\n<br />\n至於詳細係點做就可以大家諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c9364af361bbf5c69dec5148eeec611ce0b323","tid":1594911,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:13:31.000Z","msg":"叫外賣想黑警屋企咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb926ee884c5f57be356bc2a83366990b29a29bc","tid":1594911,"uid":260793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:17:34.000Z","msg":"買左野退貨\b（最好係一定可以退，而件貨要返廠repackage）"},{"pid":"eb7b98d43eb4ca024fddd77c1083929fa1f5fc21","tid":1594911,"uid":260793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:18:49.000Z","msg":"約經紀睇樓但no show"}]}